## Data model

### Spot
```
id
name
category (food | drinks | music | art | markets | community)
neighborhood
description
image
location (lat, lng — derived from address via server-side geocoding)
tags[] (optional)
owners[] — array of user references; first is the creator, additional can be added
saveCount
```

### Event
```
id
name
category (food | drinks | music | art | markets | community)
neighborhood
description
image
location (lat, lng)
date (ISO)
time
endDate (optional)
ticketUrl (optional)
ticketPrice (optional)
tags[] (optional)
hosts[] — array of user references; first is the creator, additional can be added
saveCount
isOngoing (derived: start ≤ now < end)
```

### User
```
id
name
handle
avatar (initial + color)
bio (optional)
cities[]
followerCount
followingCount
```

### Collection
```
id
name
description (optional)
ownerId
visibility (private | friends | public)
items[] — array of {itemId, itemType (spot | event), addedAt}
coverImage
saveCount
city (optional)
```

### Save
```
userId
itemId
itemType (spot | event)
savedAt
```

### Follow
```
followerId
followedId
status (pending | approved)
```

